Análisis cámaras 1-4

March - July 2019

Camara Fotoperiodo Temperatura

Dependencies

library(readr)
library(dplyr)
library(ggplot2)
library(forcats)

Load functions

source("functions.R")

Load data

cams = read_csv("data/cams_wo_outliers.csv")
## Parsed with column specification:
## cols(
##   Genotype = col_character(),
##   Camara = col_character(),
##   Repetition = col_character(),
##   Treatment = col_character(),
##   Pot = col_double(),
##   planta1 = col_character(),
##   DFAbierta = col_double()
## )

Sample distribution

mi_treat = "non-vern"

set.seed(123)

cams %>% 
  filter(Treatment == mi_treat, !is.na(DFAbierta)) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(fct_reorder(Genotype, DFAbierta), DFAbierta, 
             col = Genotype)) + 
  geom_jitter(alpha = 0.5, width = 0.3) +
  facet_wrap(~Camara) + 
  labs(x = "", y = "Days to flowering") + 
  theme(legend.position = "none", axis.text.x = element_text(size=7))

Caso Study 1

Media 3 macetas por repetición :

  • Genotipo
  • Cámara
  • Repetición
  • n, número plantas en la rep.
  • avg, media de esas plantas (días)
  • sd, desv standard del valor medio
  • Flor1, primera flor en la rep. (días)
